groom
---
Hair from Blender's https://www.blender.org/download/demo/geometry-nodes/hair_nodes-female_hair_styles.blend/

Demonstrating Bezier curve rendering & Path-traced Single-scatter Chiang Hair model

WARNING
===
Please note this is NOT standarized glTF file format, due to the usage of the following non-ratified extensions:
- EXT_foundation_curves
- EXT_foundation_materials

Refer to https://github.com/mos9527/Foundation-Blender-IO for implementation details.
